{"tid":1221588,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"救世軍高層係仆街 但盡量唔好攪到下面普通員工","createTime":"2019-06-14T08:50:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T09:35:16.000Z","uid":112300,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"212f0eab76bafd614e8ebcf6ddc94d5a78fb0cff","tid":1221588,"uid":112300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:50:52.000Z","msg":"612當日 (轉自WhatsApp)<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;各位救世軍軍官, 同事, 弟兄姊妹,<br />\n<br />\n基於今晚於灣仔金鐘一帶情況危急, 我們現開放灣仔教育及發展中心, 支援各位救世軍朋友。<br />\n<br />\n我們將有2位社工通宵駐守支援, 並提供休息地方, 水電, 基本急救用品。<br />\n<br />\n✅緊急支援時間: 由今晚至明早(6月13日) 上午9時正。( 按需要再延長緊急支援時間) <br />\n<br />\n✅地點: 香港灣仔救世軍街6號<br />\n救世軍教育及就業中心<br />\n<br />\n願天父繼續保守帶領香港<br />\n親自安慰受傷的人🙏🏾<br />\n<br />\n彼此一起為香港禱告🙏🏾🙏🏾&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日(14號)聯署聲明 (轉自TG 612 reminder)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1023028-香港-救世軍員工發聯署聲明+對救世軍「循環回收」物資深表關注\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1023028-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E6%95%91%E4%B8%96%E8%BB%8D%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E7%99%BC%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E%2B%E5%B0%8D%E6%95%91%E4%B8%96%E8%BB%8D%E3%80%8C%E5%BE%AA%E7%92%B0%E5%9B%9E%E6%94%B6%E3%80%8D%E7%89%A9%E8%B3%87%E6%B7%B1%E8%A1%A8%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpBY%2Fip2Wc62AYORpdIbS17M%3D&h=ae226780\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1023028-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E6%95%91%E4%B8%96%E8%BB%8D%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E7%99%BC%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E%2B%E5%B0%8D%E6%95%91%E4%B8%96%E8%BB%8D%E3%80%8C%E5%BE%AA%E7%92%B0%E5%9B%9E%E6%94%B6%E3%80%8D%E7%89%A9%E8%B3%87%E6%B7%B1%E8%A1%A8%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8&h=aa67aabb\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1023028-香港-救世軍員工發聯署聲明+對救世軍「循環回收」物資深表關注</a><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;救世軍僱員聯合關注聲明<br />\n<br />\n我們就救世軍總部今日(6月14日) 決定以「循環回收」方法，處理由市民捐獻支援反修例行動之物資，我們深表關注。救世軍作為社會國際福利機構，我們期望處理是次捐贈物資的方法，不要負捐贈者及市民大眾對機構的期望。救世軍向來致力締造和平，提倡社會公義，以「行公義、存憐憫」的基督精神服務社會，我們懇求救世軍接能兌現機構立場宣言。<br />\n<br />\n聯署員工現欲得悉機構對「回收物資」的處理方法，了解有關物資的去向，包括會否將公開於合適之地點讓有需要之市民領取，以便在前線工作上直接面對市民時，回應大眾及捐獻者之查詢及疑問。<br />\n<br />\n二〇一九年六月十四日<br />\n救世軍員工聯署&rdquo;"},{"pid":"e6eaa02551c4416fdcc89f0bb8255ea9c1dea00c","tid":1221588,"uid":58307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:57:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tJhrmHf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtJhrmHf.png&h=83f50132&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4fcc1030abe4121b001237fbf3624768011a3bb6","tid":1221588,"uid":112300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e6eaa02551c4416fdcc89f0bb8255ea9c1dea00c","tid":1221588,"uid":58307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:57:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tJhrmHf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtJhrmHf.png&h=83f50132&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:22:49.000Z","msg":"岩啦 要攪就對住呢d黎攪"},{"pid":"6c5808d3136c681987a7c04051a51f7a37a42b93","tid":1221588,"uid":218608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:28:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e22a6069a1c9a91a85bf07700a2c4d0fbefacc97","tid":1221588,"uid":112300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:35:16.000Z","msg":"希望大家對準目標<br />\n保住物資同時勿對下層開火"}]}